frequently asked questions

how to cancel?

To cancel your reservation, please email us. Our team will assist you further with the cancellation process and provide any necessary instructions.

is there any vacancy?

You can check the vacancy of rooms by using the "Check Availability" function on our website. Simply enter your desired dates and the system will inform you if the date and the room is available for that period.

what are payment methods?

We accept various payment methods, including major credit cards, digital wallets, and bank transfers, we also accept walk-in payment, but make sure to deposit the minimum amount beforehand. Contact us for more information.

what are the age requirements?

There is no age requirement. All guests are welcome to enjoy the hotel.
